Testing

1. Add testing libraries to project's Gemfile
  * teaspoon  (testing framework)
  * phantomjs (headless web client)
  * tapout    (test harness)
  * konacha-chai-matchers (test helpers)

2. Install Istanbul with npm (code coverage)
  * npm install -g istanbul

3. Generate stuff
  rails generate teaspoon:install --framework=mocha --coffee

4. CLI
  bundle exec teaspoon -q --format=tap_y | tapout progress
